# Explainable AI - Employee Attrition Analysis 

### Dashboard Link
[View the Power BI Dashboard](https://app.powerbi.com/groups/me/reports/baef23c4-2cf6-4eae-a433-fb452b0d842b?ctid=91b4c990-f56a-484d-a01d-998287a1d432&pbi_source=linkShare)

## Overview
This Power BI dashboard analyzes and predicts employee attrition, helping organizations identify key factors that influence attrition and implement strategies to reduce it. The interactive dashboard allows users to explore feature importance, view prediction probabilities, and understand individual predictions.

## Sample Screenshot
![Dashboard Screenshot](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/88a7e535-09fb-4800-ade7-82c906983010)

## Key Features
- **Feature Importance Visualization**: Understand the most significant factors influencing attrition.
- **Prediction Probability**: View the overall model accuracy and the breakdown of retention vs. resignation.
- **DataSet & True vs Predicted Values**: Compare actual and predicted attrition values.
- **Local Explanation for Individual Predictions**: Get detailed insights into factors influencing each prediction.
- **Interactive Controls**: Customize the view to analyze features and predictions in detail.

## Technologies Used
- **Machine Learning Models**: Python-based models for predicting attrition.
- **Model Interpretability**: Using SHAP, Shapash, and LIME for feature importance and explanations.
- **Power BI**: Visualization of model outputs for an interactive user experience.

## How This Dashboard Can Benefit Employers
By identifying the key drivers of attrition, the dashboard aids employers in understanding employee turnover and implementing targeted retention strategies, leading to reduced turnover costs and improved employee satisfaction.
